dct_title_s: Map to illustrate the journey from Hankow to Tali-Fu of Mr. A. R. Margary
dct_description_sm: Mr. Margary's route shown in red. Burmese territory and Chinese provinces are shown. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 46 (1876), pp. 172-98; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v. 46 1876
